        <abstract> 
<p>R. L. Tait has requested CD send his [Tait’s] paper on <hi rend="italic">Nepenthes</hi> to Royal Society. CD considers this a nuisance.</p> 
            <p>Certificate for G. J. Romanes.</p>
            <p>Francis’ experiments on mechanism of twisted seeds.</p>
